caption: Figure 2: Regret of EMC (Algorithm 1) and of ESTC proposed in [23], in cases of sparsity, non-crossing partitions, and non-nesting partitions.
description: The figure compares the cumulative regret of the proposed Explore Models then Commit (EMC) algorithm against the ESTC algorithm from [23] across three different scenarios: sparsity, non-crossing partitions, and non-nesting partitions.  It visually demonstrates the performance of EMC relative to a known sparse bandit algorithm in various symmetric settings.
